      class="max-w-225 text-[5rem] font-bold leading-tight mb-5 drop-shadow-md max-xl:text-[4rem] max-md:text-[2.5rem]">
      Answer the call, leave everything behind.
    </h1>

    <div class="flex justify-end">
      <a
        href="#"
        class="inline-block mr-12 mb-12 rounded-full bg-[#0dbdad] px-6 py-3 font-light text-white transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-[#27ae60] hover:-translate-y-0.5"
